## Overview

This risk register documents **10 identified risks** for a fictional 50-person SaaS company storing customer financial data. It follows the industry-standard **Likelihood × Impact** methodology aligned to the NIST Cybersecurity Framework.

The artifact demonstrates the full risk lifecycle that a GRC analyst manages: threat identification → inherent scoring → control mapping → residual scoring → treatment assignment → risk ownership.

